- "under the shadow of time" is a metaphorical expression meaning under a certain time limit;
- "golden mark" is a metaphorical way to refer to an important threshold or limit, such as the 50 units limit for elapsed time;
- "race duration" refers to the elapsed time in sailing competitions.
